about.summary: Provides extensions for package 'leaflet', many of which are used  by package 'mapview'. Focus is on functionality readily available in  Geographic Information Systems such as 'Quantum GIS'. Includes functions to display coordinates of mouse pointer position, query image values via  mouse pointer and zoom-to-layer buttons. Additionally, provides a feature  type agnostic function to add points, lines, polygons to a map.

name: r-leafem
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.0.1' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-leafem
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/leafem_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/leafem/leafem_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 61d05e3cd8a70bf35abf8fb73006f100819c291481c13bb80f0eba283be44b7a

build:
  number: 3
  noarch: generic
  script: R CMD INSTALL --build .
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-htmltools >=0.3
    - r-htmlwidgets
    - r-leaflet >=2.0.1
    - r-raster
    - r-sf
    - r-sp
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-htmltools >=0.3
    - r-htmlwidgets
    - r-leaflet >=2.0.1
    - r-raster
    - r-sf
    - r-sp

test:
  commands:
    - R -e "library('leafem')"

about:
  home: https://github.com/r-spatial/leafem
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Provides extensions for package 'leaflet', many of which are used  by package 'mapview'.
    Focus is on functionality readily available in  Geographic Information Systems such
    as 'Quantum GIS'. Includes functions to display coordinates of mouse pointer position,
    query image values via  mouse pointer and zoom-to-layer buttons. Additionally, provides
    a feature  type agnostic function to add points, lines, polygons to a map.
  license_family: MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - conda-forge/r
